high_descs: Turn right, move to the low work table at the end of the counter.
Pick up the knife from the low work table.
Slice the potato on the low work table.
Turn right, move to the table, in front of the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn left, move to the low work table at the end of the counter.
Pick up a potato slice from the low work table.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the potato slice in the refrigerator, chill it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the table, in front of the microwave.
Put the potato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around completely and walk to the right. Walk forward to the table and make a right and walk to the side table.
Pick up the knife from the side table.
Slice the potato on the side table.
Take the knife and turn around completely. Walk forward and turn to the left then right and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the knife inside.
Turn to the right and walk forward then make a left and walk to the table. Make a right and go to the side table.
Pick up a slice of potato from the side table.
Turn around completely and turn left. Walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the potato inside.
Walk forward and turn to the left then right and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the slice of potato inside.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato and place in microwave.

high_descs: Turn around to the right, walk forward a few steps, turn to the left, and then walk to the table against the wall, make a right and walk forward to the small black table.
Pick up the knife from the back of the table.
Slice the potato on the black table.
Turn right and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the knife on the plate inside.
Turn to the left and walk back to the black table.
Pick up a sliced end of the potato.
Turn to the left and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the door, place the potato on the shelf, close the door. Open the door, remove the potato, shut the door.
Turn around to the right and walk to the microwave.
Open the door, place the potato inside, behind the plate, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled potato slice into the microwave.
